ke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n</svg>\n</span><p><img src=\"https://zzypicgo.oss-cn-shanghai.aliyuncs.com/pic-go-master/img/image-20230215132358905.png-bugs_blog\" alt=\"image-20230215132358905\"></p>\n<p>到32位的时候里面还要加上频率时钟</p></blockquote>\n<blockquote><span class=\"custom-blockquote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M22 12C22 6.5 17.5 2 12 2C6.5 2 2 6.5 2 12C2 17.5 6.5 22 12 22C13.8 22 15.5 21.5 17 20.6L22 22L20.7 17C21.5 15.5 22 13.8 22 12Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M17 8.5C15.23 8.97 14.07 10.84 14.01 13.27C14 13.33 14 13.4 14 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M9 8.5C7.23 8.97 6.07 10.84 6.01 13.27C6 13.33 6 13.4 6 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n</svg>\n</span><p>数据的查询访问方式</p>\n<p>BIOS中断查询方式</p>\n<p>DOS系统中断 – 中断向量法</p>\n<p>Windows系统调用</p></blockquote>\n<h3 id=\"接口卡\"><a href=\"#接口卡\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"接口卡\"></a><font color=#FF0033 >接口卡</font></h3><blockquote><span class=\"custom-blockquote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M22 12C22 6.5 17.5 2 12 2C6.5 2 2 6.5 2 12C2 17.5 6.5 22 12 22C13.8 22 15.5 21.5 17 20.6L22 22L20.7 17C21.5 15.5 22 13.8 22 12Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M17 8.5C15.23 8.97 14.07 10.84 14.01 13.27C14 13.33 14 13.4 14 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M9 8.5C7.23 8.97 6.07 10.84 6.01 13.27C6 13.33 6 13.4 6 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n</svg>\n</span><p>计算机系统中，所有可用程序控制的设备都必须受到cpu控制，cpu对外设备都不能直接控制，如显示器，音箱，打印机等，直接控制设备工作的是插在扩展槽上的接口卡，扩展插槽通过总线同cpu相连，cpu可以直接控制这些插口卡，从而控制外设。</p>\n<p>cpu通过控制总线向接口卡发送控制命令，接口卡根据cpu的命令控制外设进行工作</p></blockquote>\n<h3 id=\"各类存储芯片\"><a href=\"#各类存储芯片\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"各类存储芯片\"></a><font color=#FF0033 >各类存储芯片</font></h3><blockquote><span class=\"custom-blockquote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M22 12C22 6.5 17.5 2 12 2C6.5 2 2 6.5 2 12C2 17.5 6.5 22 12 22C13.8 22 15.5 21.5 17 20.6L22 22L20.7 17C21.5 15.5 22 13.8 22 12Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M17 8.5C15.23 8.97 14.07 10.84 14.01 13.27C14 13.33 14 13.4 14 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M9 8.5C7.23 8.97 6.07 10.84 6.01 13.27C6 13.33 6 13.4 6 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n</svg>\n</span><p>PC机中装有多个独立的存储芯片，属于不同的部件。从属性可以划分：</p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>随机存储器(RAM)</strong>:用于存放供CPU使用的绝大部分程序和数据，主随机存储器一般由两个位置上的RAM组成，装在主板上的RAM和插在扩展插槽上的RAM(内存条)。</li>\n<li><strong>OI存储器</strong>：存放BIOS基本输入输出程序，是由主板和各类接口卡（如显卡、网卡等）厂商提供的软件系统，可以通过它利用该硬件设备进行最基本的输入输出。例如主板上的ROM中存储系统BIOS,显卡的ROI中存储显卡的IOS,网卡上装有OI存储网卡的BIOS。</li>\n<li><strong>接口卡上的RAM</strong>：某些接口卡需要对大批量输入和输出数据进行暂时存储，装有RAM。最典型的是显卡上的RAM,称为显存。我们将要显示的内容写入显存，显卡将显存中的数据向显示器输出，就会出现在屏幕上。</li>\n<li><strong>BI0S</strong>:基本输入输出程序、开机自检系统和自启动程序。</li>\n<li>CMOS内存微机主板上的BIOS芯片中一块可读写的RAM芯片，主要用来保存当前系统的硬件配置和操作人员对某些参数的设定。CMOSRAM芯片由系统通过一块后备电池供电，因此在关机状态后信息也不会丢失。</li>\n</ul></blockquote>\n<h3 id=\"接各类存储芯片\"><a href=\"#接各类存储芯片\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"接各类存储芯片\"></a><font color=#FF0033 >接各类存储芯片</font></h3><blockquote><span class=\"custom-blockquote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M22 12C22 6.5 17.5 2 12 2C6.5 2 2 6.5 2 12C2 17.5 6.5 22 12 22C13.8 22 15.5 21.5 17 20.6L22 22L20.7 17C21.5 15.5 22 13.8 22 12Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M17 8.5C15.23 8.97 14.07 10.84 14.01 13.27C14 13.33 14 13.4 14 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M9 8.5C7.23 8.97 6.07 10.84 6.01 13.27C6 13.33 6 13.4 6 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n</svg>\n</span><p><img src=\"https://zzypicgo.oss-cn-shanghai.aliyuncs.com/pic-go-master/img/image-20230215135106227.png-bugs_blog\" alt=\"image-20230215135106227\"></p></blockquote>\n<h3 id=\"内存地址空间\"><a href=\"#内存地址空间\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"内存地址空间\"></a><font color=#FF0033 >内存地址空间</font></h3><blockquote><span class=\"custom-blockquote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M22 12C22 6.5 17.5 2 12 2C6.5 2 2 6.5 2 12C2 17.5 6.5 22 12 22C13.8 22 15.5 21.5 17 20.6L22 22L20.7 17C21.5 15.5 22 13.8 22 12Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M17 8.5C15.23 8.97 14.07 10.84 14.01 13.27C14 13.33 14 13.4 14 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M9 8.5C7.23 8.97 6.07 10.84 6.01 13.27C6 13.33 6 13.4 6 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n</svg>\n</span><ul>\n<li>各类存储器都和CPU相连</li>\n<li>CPU对它们进行读或写的时候都通过控制线发出内存读写命令</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>cpu将各类存储器全部当做内存来对待，把他们总的看作一个由若干存储单元组成的逻辑存储器，这个逻辑存储器称为内存地址空间</strong></p>\n<p>16位8086:20根地址线，2^20^&#x3D;1MB内存空间 </p>\n<p>32位x86:32根地址线，2^32^&#x3D;4GB内存空间</p>\n<p>64位x64:64根地址线，2^64^,但是实际上只用了48位，256TB内存空间</p>\n<p>假如只有两根地址线，我们用二进制0和1表示内存地址编号，00,01,10,11</p>\n<p>&#x3D;&#x3D;<strong>每一个地址编号就是一个字节</strong>&#x3D;&#x3D;  每个地址编号这根线是地址线</p>\n<p>一个字节8位</p>\n<p><strong>&#x3D;&#x3D;每一个位就是一根线&#x3D;&#x3D;</strong>   这根线是数据线</p>\n<p>内存宽度就是一次可以读写多少位</p>\n<p>64位计算机就是一次可以读写64位</p>\n<ul>\n<li>CPU将系统中各类存储器看作一个逻辑存储器。</li>\n<li>所有的物理存储器被看作一个由若干存储单元组成的逻辑存储器，每个物理存储器占用一个地址段，即一段地址空间。CPU在这段地址空间读写数据，就是在相对应的物理存储器中读写数据。</li>\n</ul>\n<p>假设内存地址空间的地址段分配如下：地址<code>0~7FFFH</code>的<code>32KB</code>空间为<strong>主存储空间</strong>地址<code>8000H~9FFFH</code>的<code>8KB</code>空间为<strong>显存</strong>地址<code>A000H~FFFFH</code>的<code>24KB</code>空间为<strong>其他ROM存储器地址空间</strong></p>\n<p>CPU向地址1000H内存单元写入数据，数据就被写入主随机存储器中；CPU向地址8000H内存单元写入数据，数据被写入显存，出现在显示器上,CPU向C000H内存单元写入数据，这样的操作无效，因为C000H是ROM只读存储器单元</p>\n<p>在计算机系统里面有两种地址系统</p>\n<ol>\n<li>主板上面的插槽，就是定义好的编号，就是端口\t\t指令就是in out</li>\n<li>主存内存地址    指令就是x86其他指令</li>\n</ol>\n<p><img src=\"https://zzypicgo.oss-cn-shanghai.aliyuncs.com/pic-go-master/img/image-20230215150259170.png-bugs_blog\" alt=\"image-20230215150259170\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://zzypicgo.oss-cn-shanghai.aliyuncs.com/pic-go-master/img/image-20230215150535803.png-bugs_blog\" alt=\"image-20230215150535803\"></p>\n<p>内存地址空间的大小受地址总线宽度的限制。8086CPU地址总线为20根，即可以定位2^20^个内存单元，范围0<del>2^20^-1，地址空间大小1MB.<br>80386CPU的地址总线宽度为32，则内存地址空间为4GB.<br>基于一个计算机硬件系统编程的时候，必须知道这个计算机系统的内存地址空间的分配情况。向某类存储器读写数据时，需要知道它的第一个单元地址和最后一个单元地址。<br>8086CPU的地址分配如图：<br>&#96;0</del>9FFFF<code>的内存单元为</code>主随机存储器<code> </code>A0000<del>BFFFF<code>的内存单元为</code>显存<code> </code>C0000</del>FFFFF<code>内存单元为</code>只读存储器&#96;</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://zzypicgo.oss-cn-shanghai.aliyuncs.com/pic-go-master/img/image-20230215151316975.png-bugs_blog\" alt=\"image-20230215151316975\"></p></blockquote>\n<h2 id=\"二级标题\"><a href=\"#二级标题\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"二级标题\"></a><font color=#9400D3 >二级标题</font></h2><h3 id=\"三级标题\"><a href=\"#三级标题\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"三级标题\"></a><font color=#FF0033 >三级标题</font></h3><h4 id=\"四级标题\"><a href=\"#四级标题\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"四级标题\"></a><font color=#0000CC >四级标题</font></h4><h5 id=\"五级标题\"><a href=\"#五级标题\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"五级标题\"></a><font color=#FF00FF >五级标题</font></h5><h6 id=\"六级标题\"><a href=\"#六级标题\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"六级标题\"></a><font color=#00CC00 >六级标题</font></h6>","feature":true,"text":"组原计算机的组成硬件部分 控制寄存器 控制指令 数据寄存器 存储数据 状态寄存器 状态标志 冯诺依曼结构 缺点就是中间哪一步出错了就没有办法了 以存储为中心的计算机结构 多了一根反馈线，这个反馈线的意思是在我控制器控制外部设备的时候，你要给我一个反馈，假如我要控制输入设备，你这个...","link":"","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":"2k","symbolsTime":"2 mins."},"categories":[{"name":"组原","slug":"组原","count":4,"path":"api/categories/组原.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"逆向","slug":"逆向","count":6,"path":"api/tags/逆向.json"},{"name":"组原","slug":"组原","count":4,"path":"api/tags/组原.json"}],"toc":"<ol class=\"toc\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-1\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E7%BB%84%E5%8E%9F\"><span cla